{% comment %}
  Testimonials Section
  Student review cards with avatars and ratings
{% endcomment %}

<section class="testimonials-section" id="Testimonials" aria-label="Student Testimonials">
  <div class="container">

    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="section-header text-center">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">💬 Student Stories</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">
        What Our <span class="text-highlight">Students Say</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="section-desc">
        Real reviews from pharmacy students who transformed their exam preparation with TGPCOP PHARMA
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Rating Summary Bar -->
    <div class="testimonials-summary">
      <div class="ts-overall">
        <div class="ts-score">4.9</div>
        <div class="ts-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <div class="ts-label">Overall Rating</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ts-bars">
        <div class="ts-bar-row">
          <span class="ts-bar-label">5 ★</span>
          <div class="ts-bar"><div class="ts-bar-fill" style="width: 82%;"></div></div>
          <span class="ts-bar-pct">82%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ts-bar-row">
          <span class="ts-bar-label">4 ★</span>
          <div class="ts-bar"><div class="ts-bar-fill" style="width: 13%;"></div></div>
          <span class="ts-bar-pct">13%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ts-bar-row">
          <span class="ts-bar-label">3 ★</span>
          <div class="ts-bar"><div class="ts-bar-fill" style="width: 4%;"></div></div>
          <span class="ts-bar-pct">4%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ts-bar-row">
          <span class="ts-bar-label">2 ★</span>
          <div class="ts-bar"><div class="ts-bar-fill" style="width: 1%;"></div></div>
          <span class="ts-bar-pct">1%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ts-bar-row">
          <span class="ts-bar-label">1 ★</span>
          <div class="ts-bar"><div class="ts-bar-fill" style="width: 0%;"></div></div>
          <span class="ts-bar-pct">0%</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="ts-count-box">
        <span class="ts-count">5,200+</span>
        <span class="ts-count-label">Happy Students</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonials Grid -->
    <div class="testimonials-grid" id="TestimonialsGrid">

      <div class="testimonial-card featured-testimonial">
        <div class="testimonial-quote">"</div>
        <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">
          TGPCOP PHARMA notes are an absolute game-changer! The Pharmacology notes with color-coded diagrams helped me visualize drug mechanisms perfectly. Scored 87% in my Sem 5 exams thanks to these materials. The GPAT PYQs section is incredibly detailed with explanations for every wrong option!
        </p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="testimonial-avatar" aria-label="Priya Sharma">PS</div>
          <div class="testimonial-info">
            <strong class="testimonial-name">Priya Sharma</strong>
            <span class="testimonial-college">AIIMS BHU, B.Pharm Final Year</span>
            <span class="testimonial-product">📚 Pharmacology Complete Notes</span>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-verified">✓ Verified Purchase</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-quote">"</div>
        <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">
          Finally found notes that actually explain pharmaceutical chemistry in simple language. The synthesis route diagrams are crystal clear. Downloaded 3 subject notes and all exceeded expectations. Will definitely buy more!
        </p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="testimonial-avatar" aria-label="Rahul Verma">RV</div>
          <div class="testimonial-info">
            <strong class="testimonial-name">Rahul Verma</strong>
            <span class="testimonial-college">JSS College of Pharmacy, Mysore</span>
            <span class="testimonial-product">⚗️ Pharm Chemistry Notes</span>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-verified">✓ Verified Purchase</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-quote">"</div>
        <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">
          The 90-day GPAT study plan is brilliant! I followed it strictly and improved my mock test score from 55% to 78% in just 2 months. The infographic notes make revision super fast. Best investment for any GPAT aspirant!
        </p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="testimonial-avatar" aria-label="Ananya Mishra">AM</div>
          <div class="testimonial-info">
            <strong class="testimonial-name">Ananya Mishra</strong>
            <span class="testimonial-college">NIPER, GPAT 2024 Qualifier</span>
            <span class="testimonial-product">🎯 GPAT Complete Pack</span>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-verified">✓ Verified Purchase</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-quote">"</div>
        <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">
          As a nursing student, the pharmacology nursing notes are perfectly tailored. Drug classifications, nursing considerations, side effects — all organized beautifully. The PDF is mobile-optimized so I study during commute. Highly recommended!
        </p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="testimonial-avatar" aria-label="Kavitha R">KR</div>
          <div class="testimonial-info">
            <strong class="testimonial-name">Kavitha R.</strong>
            <span class="testimonial-college">Manipal College of Nursing</span>
            <span class="testimonial-product">🏥 Nursing Pharmacology Notes</span>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-verified">✓ Verified Purchase</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-quote">"</div>
        <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">
          Bought the Pharmaceutics PYQ bundle and completed all questions in a week. The explanations are so detailed that I didn't need any other resource. Delivery was instant and the PDF quality is top-notch. 10/10 experience!
        </p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="testimonial-avatar" aria-label="Arjun K">AK</div>
          <div class="testimonial-info">
            <strong class="testimonial-name">Arjun K.</strong>
            <span class="testimonial-college">MAHE, B.Pharm Semester 4</span>
            <span class="testimonial-product">🧪 Pharmaceutics PYQs</span>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-verified">✓ Verified Purchase</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-quote">"</div>
        <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★☆</div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">
          Good quality content with excellent value for money. Pharmacognosy notes have beautiful botanical illustrations. Would love even more MCQs in future updates, but overall a fantastic resource for every pharmacy student!
        </p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="testimonial-avatar" aria-label="Deepa S">DS</div>
          <div class="testimonial-info">
            <strong class="testimonial-name">Deepa S.</strong>
            <span class="testimonial-college">SDM College of Pharmacy</span>
            <span class="testimonial-product">🌿 Pharmacognosy Notes</span>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-verified">✓ Verified Purchase</div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div><!-- /.testimonials-grid -->

    <!-- Testimonial CTA -->
    <div class="testimonials-cta text-center">
      <a href="{{ routes.collections_url }}" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" id="TestimonialCTABtn">
        Join 5000+ Students Today →
      </a>
    </div>

  </div><!-- /.container -->
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Testimonials",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "heading",
      "label": "Section Heading",
      "default": "What Our Students Say"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Testimonials"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
